ay, April 4|url=https://www.cwtvpr.com/the-cw/shows/in-the-dark/about|location=Burbank, CA|publisher=[[The CW]]|date=January 2019|access-date=19 April 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190419185639/https://www.cwtvpr.com/the-cw/shows/in-the-dark/about|archive-date=April 19, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n==Reception==\n===Critical response===\nOn [[review aggregator]] [[Rotten Tomatoes]], the series holds an approval rating of 70% based on 10 reviews, with an average rating of 7.16/10. The website's critical consensus reads, \"Perry Mattfield is compelling as an amateur sleuth ''In the Dark'', although the series' recycling of mystery tropes and questionable treatment of physical handicaps may leave some viewers with a dim impression.\"<ref name=\"Rotten Tomatoes\" /> On [[Metacritic]], it has a weighted average score of 54 out of 100, based on 6 critics, indicating \"mixed or average reviews\".<ref>{{cite web |title=In the Dark: Season 1 |url=https://www.metacritic.com/tv/in-the-dark |website=[[Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS]] |date=2019 |accessdate=April 6, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190419133127/https://www.metacritic.com/tv/in-the-dark |archive-date=April 19, 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n===Ratings===\n<!--====Season 1====-->\n{{Television episode ratings\n| width     = 99\n\n| title1    = [[#ep1|Pilot]]\n| date1     = April 4, 2019\n| rs1       = 0.2/1\n| viewers1  = 0.87<ref name=\"1.01\"/>\n| dvr1      = 0.1\n| dvrv1     = 0.35\n| total1    = 0.3\n| totalv1   = 1.22<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/live7-ratings-week-of-april-1-this-is-us-season-3-finale-1203194579/|title=Live+7 Ratings for Week of April 1: 'This Is Us' Season 3 Finale Posts Solid Gain|last=Thorne|first=Will|website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|date=April 22, 2019|accessdate=April 22, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422221628/https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/live7-ratings-week-of-april-1-this-is-us-season-3-finale-1