gapore in 2011\n* [[Office of National Estimates]], a forerunner of the U.S. National Intelligence Council\n* [[Organisation of National Ex-Servicemen]] (O.N.E.), an organization of veterans of military service in Ireland\n\n==Music==\n===Songs===\n* \"1\", by [[Joy Zipper]]\n* [[One (Aimer song)|\"One\" (Aimer song)]], 2017\n* [[One (Ami Suzuki song)|\"One\" (Ami Suzuki song)]], 2008\n* [[One (Bee Gees song)|\"One\" (Bee Gees song)]], 1989\n* [[One (A Chorus Line song)|\"One\" (''A Chorus Line'' song)]], 1974\n* [[One (Creed song)|\"One\" (Creed song)]], 1999\n* [[One (Crystal Kay song)|\"One\" (Crystal Kay song)]], 2008\n* [[One (Ed Sheeran song)|\"One\" (Ed Sheeran song)]], 2014\n* [[One (Fat Joe song)|\"One\" (Fat Joe song)]], 2009\n* [[One (Harry Nilsson song)|\"One\" (Harry Nilsson song)]], made famous by Three Dog Night\n* [[One (JayKo song)|\"One\" (JayKo song)]], 2009\n* [[One (Metallica song)|\"One\" (Metallica song)]], 1989\n* [[One (Sky Ferreira song)|\"One\" (Sky Ferreira song)]], 2010\n* [[One (Swedish House Mafia song)|\"One\" (Swedish House Mafia song)]], 2010\n* [[One (U2 song)|\"One\" (U2 song)]], 1992\n* \"[[One (Always Hardcore)]]\", by Scooter\n* \"[[One (Blake's Got a New Face)]]\", by Vampire Weekend\n* [[O.N.E. (song)|\"O.N.E.\" (song)]], by Yeasayer\n* \"One\", by Alanis Morissette from ''[[Supposed Former Infatuation Junkie]]''\n* \"One\", by Ane Brun from ''[[It All Starts with One]]''\n* \"One\", by Epik High from ''[[Pieces, Part One]]''\n* \"One\", by Faith Hill from ''[[Cry (Faith Hill album)|Cry]]''\n* \"One\", by Ghostface Killah from ''[[Supreme Clientele]]''\n* \"One\", by Immortal Technique from ''[[Revolutionary Vol. 2]]''\n* \"One\", by Kumi Koda from ''[[Grow into One]]''\n* \"One\", by [[Lady Gaga]]\n* \"One\", by Lewis Capaldi from ''[[Divinely Uninspired to a Hellish Extent]]''\n* \"One!\", by Misia from ''[[Love Is the Message (Misia album)|Love Is the Message]]''\n* \"One\", by Parachute Band from ''[[Roadmaps and Revelati